Invocation Name: roach motel
des: Roach Motel is a memory game inspired by the classic game of Concentration and the many old motel signs that pepper the sides of the U.S. highway system. Find matching roaches by opening doors, two at a time, to empty the motel. But watch out for health citations. Get three and the game is over.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
